snippet.title: How to Graph Arccos (cosine inverse)
snippet.description:
Learn how to graph arccos (inverse cosine) in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.

0:12 Graph of the Cosine Function
0:17 Explanation of Why the Inverse of Cosine Graph is Not a Function
0:30 Restricting the Domain to Make the Inverse a Function
0:56 How to Find the Inverse of a Function Graphically
2:32 Reflection of the Graph Over the Line y=x
